{"tid":442250,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無配對公司介紹？","createTime":"2017-10-20T12:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T17:07:35.000Z","uid":143663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef37a3655dd5d4c3ca0e95dc3e764b6c50e6933b","tid":442250,"uid":143663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:14:52.000Z","msg":"出黎做野之後，生活圈子好似愈來愈細<br />\n身邊啲朋友拍拖嘅拍拖，亦有好多都結哂婚<br />\n<br />\n試過2，3次同喺apps識嘅女仔拍拖<br />\n但感覺都好似做人水泡，俾人當快餐<br />\n加上太多人借apps做生意<br />\n要認真同人交心就變得更難<br />\n人地有戒心，自己又有戒心<br />\n<br />\n想認認真真搵個另外一半計劃將來，組織家庭<br />\n有無巴絲試過搵去啲配對公司？有無邊間好介紹？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果work 的話，都唔介意洗多啲錢"},{"pid":"db96e9becbd530869577ba1070519982577f7e61","tid":442250,"uid":57953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:25:15.000Z","msg":"friend撘friend出黎飲下野 好易姐應該"},{"pid":"f8687ffa4489c628f8235d8b5cd9adc42030b490","tid":442250,"uid":128101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:43:47.000Z","msg":"出黎做野就好似變咗機械人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833a8aed0485f94105b7ec7fcbf46813d9f64c84","tid":442250,"uid":143663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>friend撘friend出黎飲下野 好易姐應該</blockquote><br />\n以前都會，以家真係少左好多, 就算係都係飲兩杯，吹兩咀個啲囉"},{"pid":"1360e9d1941d87da43bc4fbbda5226a6eda269ee","tid":442250,"uid":99941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:53:31.000Z","msg":"同感 就算配對公司一樣有做媒 真係無晒希望"},{"pid":"4a0a99d63c062076b0b7a7b4df92b72c17d8244f","tid":442250,"uid":143663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T16:54:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出黎做野就好似變咗機械人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係機械人都好啲，唔需要講情感上的需要"},{"pid":"fe4ed59bcece1843fa98f79bde504385ca145089","tid":442250,"uid":143663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同感 就算配對公司一樣有做